Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:32.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perilaku terlarang.\NItu bisa menyebabkan kerusakan mekanis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?\NMaafkan aku, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.96,0:06:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, duduklah dan istirahat dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nboleh aku berbaring di pangkuanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.47,0:06:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie?
