Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Perlu dinyalakan ulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa?
