Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.75,0:09:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh menyenangkan memiliki teman.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.48,0:09:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2, kurasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.29,0:09:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setidaknya aku harus minta maaf\Npada Tuan Arthur atas kesalahanku tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.99,0:09:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.47,0:09:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.87,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal tadi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.37,0:09:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.12,0:09:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia meminta maaf padaku lebih dulu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.12,0:09:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tidak sehat\Nsejak serangan di pesta itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.32,0:09:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu pasti terlalu memaksakan diri\Nsaat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, kamu seharusnya menjadi\Nrobot yang melindungiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, sekarang, aku mau melindungimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.25,0:09:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tanpa sadar, kamu telah menjadi\Nsesuatu yang penting bagiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sungguh luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.03,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mencintai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.73,0:10:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Awas!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyusup!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lengah tadi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.61,0:10:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jatuh dari lantai dua tak akan membunuhku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu, aku sudah bersiap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu takut setelah melihat ini, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.25,0:10:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah selama ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.53,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat Tuan Arthur dan aku akhirnya bisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.20,0:10:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat kami
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.84,0:10:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akhirnya bisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.47,0:10:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, saatnya mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.22,0:11:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}...memiliki momen yang indah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ucapan Marie-2 benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.43,0:11:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cinta memang membuat kita lebih kuat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu menang!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.49,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tatapan tanpa ekspresi\Ndan menyeramkan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.24,0:11:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bilang menyeramkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.50,0:11:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudmu sangat manis, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.26,0:11:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jatuh cinta dengan Tuan Arthur...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.48,0:11:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2, kamu dan Marie urus dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.85,0:11:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan memanggil Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.40,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, Tuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.85,0:11:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia baru saja tersenyum padaku, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.43,0:11:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu saat itu juga...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.37,0:12:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu bukan mimpi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.64,0:12:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kudengar Marie bilang dia mencintaiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku yakin itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mulai berhalusinasi tentang Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku sungguh jatuh cinta padanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat menjijikkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.45,0:12:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus segera mencari cara\Nuntuk menikahi robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.56,0:12:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika aku menikah,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}haruskah kuumumkan itu kepada dunia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.47,0:12:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, Tuan Arthur ingin bertemu denganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.56,0:12:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.57,0:12:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, bukan kamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.87,0:12:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2, cepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Muda membutuhkanmu segera.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.54,0:12:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku akan pergi juga...\N- Kamu tak perlu pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.21,0:12:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih penting\Nmenyelesaikan mencabut rumput hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.51,0:13:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2, Nyonya Rustin ada di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.23,0:13:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ingat, jangan kasar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, sepertinya kamu baik-baik saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat pagi, Nyonya Charlotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, Anda mau kopi setelah makan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.28,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentang pembicaraan kita tempo hari,\Nbagaimana menurutmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya. Luar biasa.\NMarie-2 memang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.54,0:13:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ayo.\NAku mengandalkanmu, Roy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.89,0:13:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.85,0:13:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkinkah Tuan Arthur dan Marie-2
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.73,0:13:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menjalin hubungan rahasia\Ntanpa sepengetahuanku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.04,0:14:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terlebih, Tuan Roy dan Nyonya Charlotte\Nmengakui mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.22,0:14:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di sana kamu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.53,0:14:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sangat lelah hari ini.\NKurasa aku akan tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.29,0:14:12.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, bisa pijat bahuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pijat...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2 lebih baik dalam tugas ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.51,0:14:24.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong perintahkan Marie-2 melakukannya\Nsaat dia kembali besok.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.35,0:14:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik, ayo, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.73,0:14:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anda lebih suka Marie-2 pergi ke sekolah\Ndengan Anda daripada saya, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.61,0:14:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, Marie-2 jauh lebih manis\Ndaripada saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.97,0:14:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu,\Nsaya akan masuk ke mobil dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia mudah ditebak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.34,0:14:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa aku jauh lebih manis daripada Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Langsung mencari "manis".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:54.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.41,0:14:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Sesuatu atau seseorang\Nyang membangkitkan perasaan sayang."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.47,0:15:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya banyak tugas OSIS\Nbelakangan ini, jadi agak melelahkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.58,0:15:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang sebenarnya aku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.25,0:15:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepulang sekolah, aku akan mampir\Nke taman itu dalam perjalanan pulang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.25,0:15:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Matahari terbenam di sana sangat indah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.86,0:15:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Daripada pergi dengan saya,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:23.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saya rasa Anda akan lebih bersenang-senang\Njika pergi dengan Marie-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.85,0:15:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian berdua harus pergi bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulutku...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.77,0:15:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mulutku mulai bicara sendiri...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.37,0:15:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku bisa bicara\Ndengan Tuan Arthur dengan sikap begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku bisa melihat wajah terhormatmu\Ndi pagi hari.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, kamu tampak\Nlebih melankolis hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.30,0:15:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa akan pingsan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.09,0:15:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu keren sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari berpesta lagi kapan-kapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.39,0:15:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tempo hari sangat menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.19,0:16:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan lebih menyenangkan\Njika Noah ada di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.03,0:16:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali, kita rayakan di rumahku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.93,0:16:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku baru ingat hal mendesak.\NKalian pergilah duluan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.66,0:16:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu butuh sesuatu dariku, Marie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.82,0:16:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?\NBukankah kamu selalu bersama Arthur?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari ini, aku hanya merasa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.17,0:16:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}saat bersama Tuan Arthur,\Nperasaanku menjadi sangat aneh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aneh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.93,0:16:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sebabnya aku memutuskan\Nuntuk mengawasimu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.15,0:16:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini caraku melindungi Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.85,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika ada yang kamu pikirkan,\Nkamu bisa memberitahuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu tak punya teman lain\Nuntuk diajak bicara, kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.26,0:16:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sungguh akan memberitahuku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setiap kali memikirkan Tuan Arthur\Ndekat dengan seseorang selain aku
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}atau bertemu orang lain di sudut tempat\Naku tak bisa melihat mereka,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.71,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kemarahan yang tak bisa dijelaskan\Nkurasakan muncul di dalam diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kecemburuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu emosi normal\Nbagi orang yang jatuh cinta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan kuajari cara mengatasi\Nperasaan seburuk itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu hanya perlu memastikan semua orang\Ndi sekitar kekasihmu
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.73,0:17:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menghilang sepenuhnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.13,0:17:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maka, kamu tak akan cemburu lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, tak akan ada yang tersisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.93,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga mau membunuh Arthur\Nsecepat mungkin
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}agar Marie dan aku bisa memiliki dunia\Nhanya untuk kita berdua.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya bercanda.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.75,0:17:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makin aku melihat Marie, dia makin manis.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.24,0:18:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Marie, aku datang untuk menjemputmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur masih di dalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur menghubungiku
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.48,0:18:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan bilang dia mau mampir ke taman\Nsebelum kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.49,0:18:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia memintaku menjemputmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada apa?\NSilakan masuk ke mobil.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga akan mampir ke taman\Nsebelum kembali.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pola perilakunya memang tidak terduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berurusan dengan robot cukup menantang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.68,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melaporkan ini dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.18,0:18:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Noah benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.55,0:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cemburu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}khawatir Tuan Arthur akan dibawa pergi\Noleh Marie-2.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.84,0:18:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana aku bisa begitu mengerikan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.15,0:18:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2 adalah temanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.95,0:18:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata aku sangat mencintai Tuan Arthur
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.41,0:19:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hingga kehilangan kendali atas diriku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.16,0:19:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, emosi seburuk itu muncul di hatiku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.03,0:19:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Arthur, aku menemukanmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.97,0:19:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya aku yang boleh\Nmelihat surya terbenam dengan Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur, Anda baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.48,0:19:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.48,0:19:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tak akan lolos!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.49,0:19:41.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tembak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Aku akan membalasmu!\N- Aku akan kembali!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.00,0:19:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie, tolong jaga Tuan Arthur baik-baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.63,0:19:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu merepotkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.42,0:19:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi tampaknya proyek modifikasi Marie-2\Nyang Roy dan aku kerjakan terbayar.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.64,0:20:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saran dari Bibi Charlotte memang tepat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memiliki kekuatan tembak yang berlebihan\Njuga menarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.13,0:20:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.98,0:20:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kurasa dia akan berguna bahkan saat Marie\Ndi pabrik untuk pemeliharaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.63,0:20:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belakangan ini,\Nsaya tak menghormati Anda, Tuan Arthur.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.29,0:20:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya sungguh minta maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.29,0:20:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saya kira Marie-2 berusaha\Nmenggantikan saya di sisi Tuan Arthur
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.97,0:20:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kecemburuan bergejolak di hati saya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia akan membenciku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kecemburuan?\NBerarti...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu cemburu?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.31,0:20:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, Marie-2 adalah\Npelayan robot yang hebat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.57,0:20:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, nomor satuku
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}adalah kamu, Marie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.66,0:21:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak peduli robot dengan teknologi tinggi\Nbisa sehebat apa di masa depan,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.32,0:21:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie akan selalu menjadi nomor satuku.\NItu tak akan pernah berubah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kamu tak menyadarinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.20,0:21:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}haruskah aku memperlakukanmu dengan cara\Nyang lebih istimewa mulai sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.34,0:21:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, robot juga bisa cemburu?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.01,0:21:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia manis sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.14,0:21:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuan Arthur sangat tidak adil.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.19,0:21:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Marie-2, itu agak berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.57,0:21:39.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku akan membiarkannya kali ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tujuh tindakan kasih sayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.97,0:23:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pelukan pagi, berangkat dan pulang sekolah\Nbersama sambil bergandengan tangan,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.23,0:23:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menyuapi, saling menatap,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.44,0:23:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bantal pangkuan, tepukan kepala,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.21,0:23:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan ci...